🎄🎅 Here We Go! 🎅🎄 

Our 4th Toy Drive and we're hoping it's the biggest one yet. Last year we did just over $12,000 in 2 weeks and donated Toys to those in need all over the Central Valley. Toys for Tots, Cops for Kids, Boys and Girls Club, Clovis & Newman Police Department, Modesto/Fresno CHP, and plan to do the same this year.
I figured we'd make it easy for folks who want to donate smaller amounts, you can now do so via Venmo, Pay Pal, or Apple Pay.
Any amount can be donated... $1, $5, $20, or more if you'd like, every $ counts helps
We'll have the link available (soon) in my bio for larger donors who would like to make a tax deductible donation to our 501c3. We look forward to seeing how much we can raise over the next week for the kids around the Valley! #ForTheKids

We have also partnered up with @apfresno @refynedaesthetics @projectathletesfoundation @hpanationdotcom so make sure to check their pages out, give em a follow, and let's spread some holiday cheer! 

Thank you 🎄🧸🎅

PayPal: PanelliGreg@yahoo.com
